licy-roundtable-iii-2-nato-and-nuclear-disarmament" class="bump-view" data-bump-view="tp">H-Diplo|RJISSF Policy Roundtable III-2: NATO and Nuclear Disarmament</a></li><li><a href="https://issforum.org/articlereviews/87-hearts-and-minds" class="bump-view" data-bump-view="tp">Article Review 87 on “The ‘Hearts and Minds’ Fallacy: Violence, Coercion, and Success in Counterinsurgency Warfare.”</a></li></ul></section><section id="wpcom_social_media_icons_widget-2" class="fbox swidgets-wrap widget widget_wpcom_social_media_icons_widget"><div class="sidebar-headline-wrapper"><h4 class="widget-title">Follow us on Twitter</h4></div><ul><li><a href="https://twitter.com/@HDiplo/" class="genericon genericon-twitter" target="_blank"><span class="screen-reader-text">View @HDiplo&#8217;s profile on Twitter</span></a></li></ul></section><section id="tag_cloud-4" class="fbox swidgets-wrap widget widget_tag_cloud"><div class="sidebar-headline-wrapper"><h4 class="widget-title">Tags</h4></div><div class="tagcloud"><a href="https://issforum.org/tag/2021" class="tag-cloud-link tag-link-938 tag-link-position-1" style="font-size: 15.383561643836pt;" aria-label="2021 (58 items)">2021</a>
